Alipay is a leading open platform for payments and digital services in China.

Users with a Chinese ID and bank account can use Alipay to make payments online and in person at various merchants outside of China as they travel for leisure, business, or study. 

Foreign visitors to China can connect their credit card to take advantage of Alipay’s widespread acceptance by tens of millions of merchants across the country. Alipay is not designed or intended for use by foreign users in their home country or anywhere outside of China.

Alice AI: texts, neural network, fresh ideas, knowledge, Russian-language AI chat.

Powerful Yandex AI on your phone helps with everyday chores and tackles tasks for study, work, and creativity.

Explore what the neural network can do with Alice—everything you expect from a smart chat in Russian.

Alice AI is Yandex’s family of generative models that power Alice. It includes:
- Alice AI LLM — a language model for answering questions and generating text;
- Alice AI ART — an image model for creating visuals;
- Alice AI VLM — a multimodal vision-language model for analyzing images, answering questions, and solving image-related tasks.

Ask questions, write and edit text—the Alice AI neural network responds accurately and comprehensively, and can enrich answers with images and source links. Speak by voice or type in chat.

Work with files (DOC, DOCX, PDF, TXT), structure information, and turn it into clear, usable reports. The Alice AI assistant quickly extracts key insights.

Work with photos—recognize text in images, identify objects, and get fast visual analysis. The AI chat assistant can pull data from a receipt photo, explain what’s in a shot, and convert it into an editable text format for further use.

Solve complex problems—reasoning mode produces not just quick and detailed answers, but thoughtful conclusions. You get well-founded solutions with expert-level analysis.

Create compelling English-language copy, ask questions, translate, and edit. Yandex Alice’s AI assistant helps draft anything—from personal emails and school assignments to business proposals.

Find inspiration: generate new project ideas, run brainstorms, craft descriptions and messages, and build your own text templates. Let Alice handle the routine. The AI assistant can write a letter, a script for an event or talk, suggest a post title, or even a name for your pet.

Create images and AI video—Yandex ART generates visuals or animates photos on request. Alice helps you produce striking social posts, a logo, or a birthday card.

Use AI chat for professional work. The assistant helps with programming and code, offering multiple solution approaches. Alice AI teaches logic, explains logical problems clearly, and shares interesting facts. Get advice and recommendations on any topic—Alice answers in detail, suggests step-by-step actions, and helps you plan.

Ask questions, type text, attach photos, videos, and files—or talk through the camera in real time with Live Mode. With the Pro option, show Alice what you see in Live Mode and get instant answers and ideas. Just open the Alice AI app and point your phone’s camera at whatever you want to learn about.

Alice AI can be your guide to landmarks, your kitchen co-pilot for “what can I cook with this?”, or your stylist for picking shoes to match your trousers. Ask anything and switch topics as needed. The neural network keeps context, recognizes objects in the frame, and delivers fast, in-depth answers.

Sajda – The Complete Islamic App, Ad-Free Since 2012  
Trusted by over 4 million Muslims around the world

Sajda is your all-in-one companion for a focused, fulfilling worship experience. Free of ads for over a decade and loved by millions globally, Sajda helps you stay spiritually connected—wherever life takes you.

Whether you're checking prayer times at work, reading the Quran while commuting, or finding the Qibla while traveling, Sajda supports your daily worship with clarity and ease.

Why millions choose Sajda:

Prayer Times  
Accurate and scholar-approved prayer timings based on your location. Fully adjustable, with countdowns to the next salah.

Adhan Alerts  
Get ready for prayer with peaceful calls from the muezzin—or choose your own sound. Includes guided rak’ah prompts.

Quran  
Read the Holy Quran with translations and transliterations. Save favorite ayahs, add personal notes, and pick your font. Effortlessly resume where you left off.

Dhikr  
Count your daily dhikr with a built-in counter. Listen to beautiful du’a recitations and join group dhikr sessions. More features are on the way, inshaAllah.

Qibla Direction  
Use the animated compass or map view (standard or satellite) to instantly find the Qibla—no matter where you are.

Widgets & Prayer Calendar  
Keep prayer times on your home screen. Share personalized salah schedules with family and friends.

Live from Makkah  
Watch real-time broadcasts from Masjid al-Haram and feel spiritually closer to the heart of Islam.

More than an app — a global movement  
Sajda has been ad-free since day one. Our mission is to connect 1 billion Muslims through simple, meaningful digital worship. Upgrade to Sajda Plus for offline Quran access, exclusive recitations, and to support prayer education worldwide.

Download Sajda now  
Join millions of Muslims from Istanbul to Jakarta, Tashkent to Barcelona. Download today and experience your faith with focus.

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is your comprehensive Islamic companion, designed to support your daily spiritual journey. With essential features like accurate prayer time reminders, Azkar collection, and Qibla direction, it helps strengthen your faith and manage your daily worship seamlessly.

* Qibla Direction: Find the Qibla direction accurately, no matter where you are. The integrated Qibla compass ensures precise alignment for your prayers.
* Quran Access: Read and reflect on the Holy Quran directly within the app. The clear and user-friendly interface allows for easy navigation between chapters and verses, supporting your daily recitation goals.
* Prayer Reminders: Never miss a prayer with customizable reminders that fit your routine. Whether it's a gentle nudge for Fajr or a midday reminder for Dhuhr, you'll stay connected to your worship schedule.

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is designed to be your trusted spiritual companion, integrating faith seamlessly into your daily routine. Whether you're managing prayer times, reflecting on Quranic verses, or seeking solace in Azkar and Duas, this app supports your spiritual growth and devotion.

Download now and experience the convenience, guidance, and fulfillment of having a complete Islamic companion right at your fingertips. Stay connected to your faith, no matter where life takes you.

Breathing is one of the simplest ways to restore balance, and research shows that structured breathing practices can lower stress, improve focus, and support emotional stability. This app turns those techniques into easy daily routines that fit into real life.

On the home screen, you will see your icon, nickname, and a clear progress indicator. From here you can access breathing practices, daily tasks, your profile, app info, and settings. A statistics window lets you review your activity and see how consistent you have been.

The breathing section includes four guided methods:
• Abdominal breathing, proven to lower nervous system activity, helps reduce anxiety and return the body to a resting state.
• Rhythmic breathing balances internal pace, with short pauses after inhale and exhale that signal the body to slow down.
• Expansive breathing creates a sense of lightness by filling the chest and abdomen before releasing tension with a longer exhale.
• Releasing breath uses short inhales and extended exhales to quickly reduce irritation and emotional overload.

Each technique comes with step-by-step instructions, timing counts, and suggestions on when to use it whether before sleep, during moments of distraction, or in times of stress.

Daily tasks keep practice consistent without being repetitive. You may be asked to spend five minutes with abdominal breathing in the morning, try rhythmic cycles during a break, or combine expansive breathing with gentle stretches. At the end of the month, you can complete a “breathing session” that blends all four methods in sequence.

Your profile tracks either time or repetitions, depending on your preference. You can upload a photo, edit your nickname, and view personal analytics. Notifications, sound, and vibration can be adjusted in settings. An information section provides context on mental health and why breathing techniques are an evidence-based way to restore balance.

This is not just about exercises it is about creating a toolkit you can return to whenever you need clarity, calm, or energy. Each short session adds up, helping you build a reliable rhythm of stability throughout your day.

Циан — ведущий сервис в России для тех, кто ищет недвижимость для аренды или покупки. Здесь можно легко найти жилье на короткий или длительный срок, а также предложения по продаже квартир, домов и коммерческих объектов. 

Наш сервис предлагает широкий выбор жилья как в новостройках, так и на вторичном рынке, включая уникальные проекты квартир и детальные планировки. Все объявления проходят модерацию, что гарантирует их актуальность и достоверность.

Более 80 фильтров для удобного поиска квартир и домов
Ищите квартиры и дома для покупки или аренды с помощью интерактивной карты в приложении — просто выберите нужный район. Более 80 фильтров помогут найти подходящий вариант с учетом инфраструктуры и характеристик жилья. Фильтруйте по цене, количеству комнат и другим параметрам. Сохраняйте поиск и добавляйте понравившиеся объекты в избранное, чтобы не упустить выгодные предложения от собственников без скрытых комиссий.

Широкий выбор квартир в новостройках
Просто задайте параметры поиска: срок сдачи ЖК, этаж, площадь, наличие или отсутствие отделки, а также цену за всю квартиру или за квадратный метр. Если вы предпочитаете покупку от застройщиков или вам важна комнатность вашей квартиры, для вас доступны специальные фильтры. Таким образом, вы сможете легко найти свой идеальный ЖК.

Умный Циан-помощник для поиска недвижимости
Циан-помощник — интеллектуальный сервис, который покажет подходящие варианты, поможет с ипотекой, сообщит о новых объявлениях, сэкономит время и поможет принять решение. Поручите поиск жилья искусственному интеллекту — задавайте критерии, а помощник пришлет вам подходящие варианты.

Оформление ипотеки
Заполните одну анкету и отправьте её сразу в 7 банков — всего за 2 минуты вы получите персональные предложения по ипотеке. Сравните условия и выберите то, что подходит именно вам. Ипотека — это первый шаг к вашему будущему дому или квартире. Начните путь к мечте уже сегодня!

Посуточная аренда квартир, домов и коттеджей
Удобный поиск жилья для посуточной аренды — квартиры, дома, коттеджи и комнаты. Смотрите варианты на карте или в списке, фильтруйте по цене, району, типу и удобствам. Легко сравнивайте объекты и выбирайте лучшее - в центре, у метро, у моря или рядом с достопримечательностями.

Размещение объявлений о сдаче и продаже недвижимости

Добавляйте и удаляйте самые разные устройства, от колонок с Алисой до кондиционеров, меняйте названия и расположение — и настраивайте, как вам нравится.

Поручите часть домашних дел Алисе. Достаточно один раз настроить расписание, и она будет сама поливать цветы и включать перед сном увлажнитель.

• СЦЕНАРИЙ В ОДНО КАСАНИЕ
Добавьте сценарий в виджет — и кнопка управления будет всегда под рукой, на главном экране телефона.

developer: Hangzhou Dong Bin Information Technology Co., Ltd.
description:
The DMSS app can enhance your security management efficiency. You can watch real-time surveillance videos and play them back anytime, anywhere, via Wi-Fi or cellular networks. If a device alarm is triggered, DMSS will immediately push an instant notification to you.

DMSS offers：
1. Real-time Live View：
You can view real-time surveillance videos from the added devices anytime, anywhere, to help you better monitor the safety of your home environment.

2. Video Playback：
You can quickly find the events you care about by date and event category, and playback the required historical video footage.

3. Instant Alarm Notifications：
You can subscribe to different alarm events according to your needs.  When an event is triggered, you will immediately receive the message notification.

4. Device Sharing
You can share the device with family members for shared use and assign them different usage permissions.

5. Alarm Hub
You can add a variety of peripheral accessories to the alarm hub to provide warnings for potential theft, intrusion, fire, water damage, and other situations. In case of an unforeseen event, DMSS can immediately activate alarms and send out danger notifications.

6. Visual Intercom
You can add visual intercom devices to engage in video calls between the device and the DMSS, as well as perform functions like locking and unlocking.

7. Access Control
You can add access control devices to check the current status of doors and view unlock records, as well as perform remote unlocking operations on the doors.
